  <num>22-4513</num>
  <heading>Exceptions.</heading>
  <text>Except as provided in <cite path="§22-4502">§ 22-4502</cite>, <cite path="§22-4504|(b)">§ 22-4504(b)</cite>, and <cite path="§22-4514|(b)">§ 22-4514(b)</cite>, this chapter shall not apply to toy or antique pistols unsuitable for use as firearms.</text>
